high_descs: Turn right, walk to the sink
Grab the knife by the sink
Turn around, walk to the white stove
Put the knife in the pan on the stove
Take the pan with the knife
Turn around, walk to the white table
Put the pan with knife on the table by the cabbage
anns.task_desc: Put the pan from stove and knife from the sink to the white table

high_descs: Turn to go to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter in front of the sink.
Take the knife and go to the stove.
Put the knife on the pan that is on the stove in the left front corner.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it  that is on the stove on the left front corner.
Turn to go to the table with the pan with the knife in it.
Put the pan with the knife in it on the table in front of the coffee maker and to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with the knife on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, then go to the sink.
Pick up the knife nearest to you.
Turn right, go toward the trash bin, then turn right, the go to the stove and turn left.
Place the knife in the pot on the left corner of the stove.
Pick up the pot on the left corner of the stove.
Turn left, then left again, go forward, then turn left to face the table with the coffee maker.
Place the pot on the table, in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it on the table.
